Description:
FORGET TURN-KEY HOUSES, TURNBRIDGE IS WHERE IT'S AT
"Why wait for years for land to title and your house to build when you can move here straight away?"
Settle down in the popular Aspect/Arcadia estate with a modern four bedroom home. The Watersun property has only just celebrated its fourth birthday so it holds so much potential for investors and owner-occupiers alike.
Located just off the freeway, the property is so close to recently established shops and public transport and will be serviced well by the Cardinia Road widening.
The property itself features:
- Four bedrooms, master with en-suite and walk-in robe;
- Open plan living/dining room;
- Modern kitchen with modern appliances;
- Double car garage with remote access;
- Heating and cooling;
- Landscaped gardens.
All the benefits of a turnkey property but ready to move in right away.
